  "texts": [
    "This customized method ensures the chosen methodology aligns with the application's unique characteristics and operational exigencies.• Iterative Optimization and Evaluation: Adopting an iterative refinement process for the selected algorithm is essential.",
    "This process entails continuous evaluation and optimization to align with evolving application needs and computational landscapes.",
    "Such a dynamic method not only ensures sustained accuracy in WCET estimation but also enhances the system's adaptability and resilience to changes.• Exploration of Hybrid Methodologies: The intersection between GA and RL presents a fertile ground for innovation.",
    "Future research should delve into hybrid methodologies that integrate GA's solution space exploration with RL's adaptive learning capabilities.",
    "This exploration could lead to methodologies with enhanced robustness, efficiency, and applicability across a spectrum of real-time systems.• Broadening the Application Spectrum: Extending the application of these methodologies beyond CD and 6-DOF robotic scenarios to other realtime system domains could offer valuable insights."
  ]
}